---

---

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24" id="faq">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6">
            Common <span class="text-gradient-main">Questions</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
            Everything you need to know about the Growth Ecosystem.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- Item 1 -->
        <details
            class="group glass-panel rounded-xl overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
        >
            <summary
                class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-bold text-white"
            >
                <span>How is this different from a regular agency?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                    <svg
                        fill="none"
                        height="24"
                        shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
                    >
                </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="text-gray-400 px-6 pb-6 pt-0 leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    Traditional agencies sell services (inputs). We sell
                    outcomes (outputs). We don't just "run your ads"; we install
                    a complete infrastructure—creative production, media buying,
                    and conversion optimization—that you eventually own. Plus,
                    our incentives are aligned: we make the most money when you
                    scale, not just by charging a retainer.
                </p>
            </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Item 2 -->
        <details
            class="group glass-panel rounded-xl overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
        >
            <summary
                class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-bold text-white"
            >
                <span>What is the "Risk Reversal" guarantee?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                    <svg
                        fill="none"
                        height="24"
                        shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
                    >
                </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="text-gray-400 px-6 pb-6 pt-0 leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    We are performance-based. If we don't hit the agreed-upon
                    KPIs (ROAS, CPA, or Revenue Lift) within the first 90 days,
                    we work for free until we do. We take on the downside risk
                    so you don't have to.
                </p>
            </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Item 3 -->
        <details
            class="group glass-panel rounded-xl overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
        >
            <summary
                class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-bold text-white"
            >
                <span>Do I own the creative assets?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                    <svg
                        fill="none"
                        height="24"
                        shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
                    >
                </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="text-gray-400 px-6 pb-6 pt-0 leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    100%. Unlike most agencies that hold your IP hostage, every
                    video, image, and landing page we build is your property
                    forever. We are building <em>your</em> asset library.
                </p>
            </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Item 4 -->
        <details
            class="group glass-panel rounded-xl overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden"
        >
            <summary
                class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer text-lg font-bold text-white"
            >
                <span>What is the minimum requirement to work with you?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                    <svg
                        fill="none"
                        height="24"
                        shape-rendering="geometricPrecision"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg
                    >
                </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="text-gray-400 px-6 pb-6 pt-0 leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                    We typically work with brands doing at least $50k/month in
                    revenue who have validated product-market fit. Our ecosystem
                    is designed to take you from $1M to $10M+. If you are
                    earlier stage, we have a specific "Incubator" track—apply
                    via the audit to see if you qualify.
                </p>
            </div>
        </details>
    </div>
</section>
